requirement: This code is intended to implement a control mechanism for setting the extension and retraction percentages of proportional valves for ground or overhead tracks based on input level, index, and percentage values.
provide_code:
FUNCTION_BLOCK CommandExecutor
VAR_INPUT
	level		:INT;			//1->地轨	2->天轨
	idx			:INT;			//挡板索引编号
	percent		:REAL;			//比例阀百分比 传入-100~+100
END_VAR
VAR_OUTPUT
END_VAR
